---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service — CommerceForge"
  description="Terms of Service for CommerceForge, the Shopify Hydrogen starter kit."
  noindex={true}
>
  <!-- NAV -->
  <header class="border-b border-zinc-800 px-6 py-4">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="font-semibold text-zinc-50 transition hover:text-indigo-400"
        >CommerceForge</a
      >
      <a href="/#pricing" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 transition hover:text-zinc-50"
        >Pricing →</a
      >
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <main class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mb-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-50">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mb-12 text-sm text-zinc-500">Last updated: March 2026 · CommerceForge</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none space-y-10 text-zinc-300">

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By purchasing or downloading CommerceForge ("the Product") you agree to be bound by
            these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree, do not purchase or use the
            Product. These Terms constitute the entire agreement between you and CommerceForge
            ("we", "us") regarding the Product.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">2. License</h2>
          <p>
            Upon purchase, we grant you a non-exclusive, non-transferable, perpetual license to
            use the Product for the number of stores specified in your pricing tier:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
            <li><strong class="text-zinc-200">Starter (€199)</strong> — 1 store.</li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-zinc-200">Pro (€449)</strong> — up to 5 stores.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-zinc-200">Agency (€1,499)</strong> — unlimited stores.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You may not resell, sublicense, or redistribute the source code as a standalone
            starter kit or template product.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">3. Permitted Use</h2>
          <p>You may:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
            <li>Modify the code to build Shopify storefronts for yourself or your clients.</li>
            <li>Deploy to any hosting provider, including Shopify Oxygen.</li>
            <li>Remove or replace the CommerceForge branding in delivered projects.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">You may not:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
            <li>Redistribute, resell, or share the original source code with third parties.</li>
            <li>
              Use the Product to build a competing starter kit, theme, or template product.
            </li>
            <li>
              Claim authorship of the base framework without substantial modification (≥50% of
              codebase).
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">4. Delivery</h2>
          <p>
            After successful payment, you will receive access to the private GitHub repository
            and/or a downloadable ZIP archive via the email address provided at checkout.
            Delivery is typically immediate but may take up to 24 hours in exceptional cases.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">5. Refund Policy</h2>
          <p>
            Customers may request a refund within 7 days of purchase by contacting us at
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@commerceforge.dev"
              class="text-indigo-400 transition hover:text-indigo-300"
              >hello@commerceforge.dev</a
            >. Refunds may be granted in cases such as duplicate purchases, delivery or access
            issues we are unable to resolve, or material issues with the Product. We reserve the
            right to refuse refund requests where the Product has been successfully delivered and
            no material issue is present.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">6. Support</h2>
          <p>
            All plans include 30 days of email support from the date of purchase. Support covers
            setup questions and bugs in the original codebase. Custom development, feature
            requests, and integration work are outside the scope of included support and may be
            quoted separately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">7. Updates</h2>
          <p>
            License holders receive all patch and minor version updates free of charge for 12
            months from the date of purchase. Major version upgrades may be offered at a
            discounted price.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">8. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The Product is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We do not guarantee
            that the Product will be error-free, uninterrupted, or fit for any particular
            purpose. Your use of the Product is at your sole risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, CommerceForge shall not be liable for any
            indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the
            Product, even if advised of the possibility of such damages. Our total liability
            shall not exceed the amount you paid for the Product.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">10. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by the laws of Italy. Any disputes shall be subject to the
            exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Italy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on
            this page with an updated date. Continued use of the Product after changes
            constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50">12. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about these Terms, contact us at
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@commerceforge.dev"
              class="text-indigo-400 transition hover:text-indigo-300"
              >hello@commerceforge.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="border-t border-zinc-800 px-6 py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 sm:flex-row">
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-zinc-50">CommerceForge</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">© 2026 CommerceForge. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-zinc-500">
        <a href="/terms" class="text-zinc-300">Terms</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="transition hover:text-zinc-300">Privacy</a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@commerceforge.dev" class="transition hover:text-zinc-300"
          >hello@commerceforge.dev</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>
